---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Law Firm Automation & Intake Workflows | Clio & DocuSign | LogicLoom"
  description="Automate client intake, document collection, and retainer renewals. We integrate Clio, DocuSign, and Office 365 to let your attorneys practice law, not data entry."
>
  <div x-data="{ modalOpen: false }">

    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-20 px-6 overflow-hidden z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
        
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-8 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/60 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-800 uppercase tracking-widest">Industry: Legal Services</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-[1.05]">
          Billable Hours. <br />
          <span class="text-gray-400">Not Admin Hours.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 font-normal max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Your attorneys should be practicing law, not chasing signatures or manually creating folders. We automate client intake, document collection, and retainer renewals.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <button @click="modalOpen = true" class="bg-slate-900 text-white text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-gray-400/20 active:scale-95 border border-slate-700">
            Automate My Firm
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-y border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The "Administrative" Leak</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><i class="ph ph-file-pdf text-xl"></i></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Intake Friction</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Potential clients drop off because your intake PDF is impossible to fill out on a smartphone. You lose the case before it starts.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><i class="ph ph-phone-incoming text-xl"></i></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">The "Status Check" Call</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Clients calling every 48 hours just to ask "what's happening?" This disrupts deep work and non-billable time accumulates.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><i class="ph ph-timer text-xl"></i></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Uncaptured Time</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Attorneys forgetting to log the 15-minute phone call or the 3 emails sent from their phone. That's revenue evaporation.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The LogicLoom Fix</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-amber-400"><i class="ph ph-check-circle"></i> <span>Web Form &rarr; Create Clio Contact/Matter</span></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-amber-400"><i class="ph ph-check-circle"></i> <span>Status Change &rarr; Auto-SMS Update to Client</span></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-amber-400"><i class="ph ph-check-circle"></i> <span>Document Upload &rarr; Auto-Save to Case Folder</span></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-amber-400"><i class="ph ph-check-circle"></i> <span>Meeting Ended &rarr; AI Prompt to Log Time</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-amber-500 to-transparent opacity-50"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-ios-bg">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">Secure integrations for your firm</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 grayscale opacity-60 hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl text-gray-600"><i class="ph ph-scales"></i> Clio</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl text-gray-600"><i class="ph ph-gavel"></i> PracticePanther</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl text-gray-600"><i class="ph ph-signature"></i> DocuSign</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl text-gray-600"><i class="ph ph-microsoft-word-logo"></i> Office 365</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl text-gray-600"><i class="ph ph-list-checks"></i> Typeform</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-12">The ROI of Efficiency</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">30%</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">More Billable Time</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">2x</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Faster Retainer Signings</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">&darr; 80%</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Inbound "Status" Calls</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white text-center relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Modernize your practice.</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10">We'll map your client intake lifecycle and identify the exact bottlenecks costing you billable hours.</p>
        <button @click="modalOpen = true" class="bg-amber-600 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-amber-500 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-amber-900/50">
          Audit My Firm
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div x-show="modalOpen" style="display:none;" class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center px-4" x-transition.opacity>
      <div @click="modalOpen = false" class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>
      <div class="relative bg-white w-full max-w-lg rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-4 border-b border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Book Law Firm Audit</h3>
          <button @click="modalOpen = false" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-black"><i class="ph ph-x text-xl"></i></button>
        </div>
        <div class="h-[500px] w-full bg-white">
           <iframe src="https://cal.com/logicloomsystems-cal/15min?embed=true" style="width:100%;height:100%;border:none;"></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>